title: Blazing 5 - Week 5
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 5
description:
Colin talks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com & Fox Sports Radio about his Blazing 5 picks to find out which ones the sharps in Vegas agree or disagree with. 

This week's games:

Panthers @ Falcons

Jaguars @ Texans

Rams @ Washington

Colts @ Browns

Vikings @ Seahawks


Plus, Colin gives out a bonus pick not in his Blazing 5
